  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Harriniva Adventure Resort is on a full board basis. Your first meal will be <span>dinner on arrival day and last meal will be breakfast on departure day.</span></p>
<p>Each day you can enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet with a range of hot and cold options. In the evening you can enjoy a three course evening meal, the menu combines modern tastes with a Lappish touch. One evening you'll have a special Christmas dinner. Soft drinks and juice wristband included for children. There's also <span>complimentary coffee and tea in the hotels main restaurant, plus a range of soft drinks available.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
