  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are cosy-log style rooms, and sleep up to three people with three single beds. These rooms are available for single use on selected dates, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Sauna Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people in a cosy cabin style room. These rooms have a room with a double bed, and an open plan seating area with a sofa bed - suitable for one adult or two children. These rooms also have a private sauna.</p>
<p><strong>Wilderness</strong> <strong>Suites </strong>sleep up to five people in a duplex style apartment. These suites have a double bed on the mezzanine level and an additional sofa bed - suitable for two adults or three children downstairs. These suites also have a mini-fridge and ecological Finnish hair and body products.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="has-small-font-size">Seating area</li>
<li class="has-small-font-size">Bathroom with toilet and shower</li>
<li class="has-small-font-size">Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
